# 🚀 Workforce Management API

This is a Spring Boot backend application designed for managing workforce tasks. It demonstrates CRUD operations with in-memory storage, uses DTOs and mappers for data flow, and is fully Dockerized for deployment.

---

## 📌 Features

- ✅ Create a new task
- ✅ Reassign a task to another assignee
- ✅ Fetch task by ID
- ✅ List all tasks
- ✅ In-memory data storage using `HashMap`
- ✅ REST API using Spring Boot
- ✅ Docker support for containerized deployment

---

## ⚙️ Tech Stack

- Java 17
- Spring Boot 3.x
- Gradle
- Lombok
- Docker

